name: Staked Resolv
reason:
Resolv is a protocol maintaining USR, a stablecoin natively backed by Ether (ETH) and Bitcoin (BTC) and pegged to the US Dollar.

stRESOLV token allows its holders to participate in the governance of Resolv. Stakers are enabled to receive staking rewards and Points Boost in Resolv Points activities.
